New Records: Russell Westbrook recorded his 18th career game with at least 10 assists off the bench, overtaking Earl Watson for the seventh-most such games in NBA history.
Key Match Events: Jamal Murray returned to the starting lineup after missing three games due to concussion protocol and scored 28 points, with six assists and four rebounds.
Russell Westbrook recorded 10 assists in just 24 minutes off the bench, showcasing his playmaking ability and strong defensive play.
